When you get your mana regen up high enough i.e.  MC3, FT 10 +, the 15 sec cast time on them is just too horendous to even bother...... <br>
<br>
I've got mana conservation III, so add on to that mage focus items for Spell haste and improved DD, further add onto that all the FT items and MC, and elemental form : water, and the 15 sec cast time on boots is prety much not worth it anymore for soloing.<br>
<br>
